Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.88,0:00:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm bored!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.75,0:00:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.96,0:00:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I've read all these books already.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.55,0:00:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.30,0:00:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm bored. I wanna do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.26,0:00:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Things have been so slow around here I don—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.14,0:00:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight! Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.31,0:00:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, Twilight, darling, oh, thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.98,0:00:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that my—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.82,0:00:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Whew! Got here as fast I c—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.99,0:00:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Finally!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.58,0:00:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been summoned!\NI wonder where the map wants us to—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.58,0:00:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, Twilight...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.62,0:01:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do ya think?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.18,0:01:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Manehattan! We've been called to Manehattan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.39,0:01:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I've simply been dying to go back for a visit!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.31,0:02:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, I return...with a purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.10,0:02:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmmm. It looks like you've been summoned
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.44,0:02:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,to this particular neighborhood here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.56,0:02:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We're off to solve a friendship problem
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.69,0:02:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,in one of the busiest and most vibrant cities in all of Equestria!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.36,0:02:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this exciting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.82,0:02:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems a hair odd, though, don't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.62,0:02:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Map callin' me to a big city like Manehattan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.79,0:02:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You may be more of a country pony at heart, Applejack,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.58,0:02:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,but the map picked you two because you're the best ponies to
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.21,0:02:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,tackle this particular mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.59,0:02:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But how will we even know what our mission's supposed to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.42,0:02:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That neighborhood probably has twice
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.84,0:02:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,as many ponies as all of Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.59,0:02:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Pff. Kch. Ts! More like three times!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.97,0:02:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, it's not only home to the Haypacking District,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.52,0:02:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,it's also home to the Fashion District!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.90,0:02:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, shame you weren't called as well, though, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.86,0:02:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You did end up quite a fan of the hustle
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.57,0:02:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and bustle of Manehattan on our last visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.94,0:02:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's such an exciting city,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.11,0:02:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and there's still so much I'd like to do there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.37,0:03:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So many museums and historical landmarks to visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.49,0:03:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to mention all the libraries!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.83,0:03:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is your mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.67,0:03:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry 'bout me.\NI've got plenty of...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.96,0:03:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,books...to keep me...busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.88,0:03:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I just remembered something!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.38,0:03:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sisterhooves Social!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.01,0:03:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have to miss it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.76,0:03:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No tellin' how long we'll be in Manehattan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.31,0:03:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I sure hope Apple Bloom and Sweetie Belle aren't too upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.62,0:03:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Manehattan, what you do to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.88,0:03:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Darling, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.42,0:03:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ponies move so fast here.\NNot at all like back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.80,0:04:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Eyes peeled, ears open.\NEyes peeled, ears open.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.48,0:04:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember, Applejack, you're in the big city now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.49,0:04:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No moseying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.99,0:04:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You gotta walk with speed and confidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.33,0:04:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoo-hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.08,0:04:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Move it!\NSorry 'bout that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.88,0:04:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, git outta my way!\NSorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.54,0:04:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch it!\NHeh...oh dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.55,0:04:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Butter my biscuits,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.92,0:04:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I can barely cross the street in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.97,0:04:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,How'm I supposed to help solve a—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.47,0:04:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.56,0:04:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I think this is the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.56,0:04:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No! No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.73,0:04:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.19,0:04:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That hat clashes with your mane,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.90,0:04:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,not to mention it's far too large
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.23,0:04:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and will undoubtedly obstruct your vision.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.03,0:04:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear, none of these will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.78,0:05:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Applejack!\NAw, good timing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.12,0:05:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. This will do splendidly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.54,0:05:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's lovely!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.17,0:05:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, how much would you like for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.92,0:05:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no no, please, please, keep it.\NI can always make another.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.30,0:05:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.05,0:05:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And you thought we wouldn't discover our purpose here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.30,0:05:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm pretty sure that wasn't it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.06,0:05:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.85,0:05:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I just saved that poor pony from committing a terrible crime of fashion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.44,0:05:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, she could've been meeting a friend
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.61,0:05:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,who would've laughed at her new hat
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.07,0:05:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and then their friendship could've been ruined forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.07,0:05:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And...mmm...it's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.45,0:05:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Did your cutie mark glow signifyin' a job well done?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.83,0:05:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ye— No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.62,0:05:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose it didn't.\NStill, a disaster was averted!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.79,0:05:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Averted? You just lost me a paying customer!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.63,0:05:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my! Oh, I-I-I-I-I'm s-so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.55,0:06:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I never meant to—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.76,0:06:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Beat it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.80,0:06:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, please accept my sincerest apologies for the misunderstanding,\NBeat it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.84,0:06:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, please accept my sincerest apologies for the misunderstanding,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.43,0:06:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and, might I add, what a lovely establishment you have here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.27,0:06:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right, Applejack.\NThe search continues.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.90,0:06:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, 'scuse me, I was wonderin'...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.61,0:06:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, friendship problem, anypony?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.78,0:06:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,See, we've been sent here to..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.82,0:06:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,A-A map summoned us and, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.78,0:06:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If you could just take a moment to, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.45,0:06:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Friendship advice!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.12,0:06:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Anypony looking for friendship advice!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.42,0:06:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Good grief!\NThis isn't working!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.59,0:06:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure what we're supposed to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.21,0:06:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, I'm still not even sure what the map called me here for.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.97,0:06:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, try not to worry, Applejack.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.14,0:06:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The map picked us for a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.22,0:06:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Although, how we're supposed to uncover that reason, I haven't a clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.43,0:06:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't possibly approach every single pony
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.85,0:06:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,in town until we find out what we're meant to DO!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.98,0:07:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,"Please help us restore our long-lost but beloved tradition,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.28,0:07:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,the Midsummer Theater Revival.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.53,0:07:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a guest performance by a local theater troupe, the Method Mares,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.99,0:07:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,as well as games, food, and much, much more.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.04,0:07:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This event promises to bring our broken neighbors together
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.62,0:07:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and restore our sense of community
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.29,0:07:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,but there's so much to do and we need your help." Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.79,0:07:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Darling, this is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.05,0:07:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The contact on the flyer is Coco Pommel!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.47,0:07:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.09,0:07:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the one who got a job makin' costumes
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.89,0:07:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,for that designer friend o' yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.85,0:07:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ou see?! This must be why the map called us here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.56,0:07:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and you were so worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.60,0:07:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I suppose it's at least worth lookin' into...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.15,0:07:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,that is, if we ever get off this street corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.82,0:07:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you found my flyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.32,0:07:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Quite a coincidence, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.54,0:07:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Applejack and I were specifically summoned here to be of service,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.54,0:07:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and you, my dear friend, are in need of help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.92,0:08:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no coincidence, darling.\NIt's fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.84,0:08:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This Midsummer Theatre Revival –
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.84,0:08:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,what is it, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.38,0:08:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,An outdoor play held in the community park.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.18,0:08:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Many moons ago, local theatre troupes would perform,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.52,0:08:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and ponies in the neighborhood would help
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.18,0:08:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,make the costumes, and design setpieces,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.85,0:08:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,prepare food to share during the performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.98,0:08:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Y'all do look like you're enjoyin' each others' company.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.61,0:08:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Kinda reminds me of Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.36,0:08:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounds lovely, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.61,0:08:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It was,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.86,0:08:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,up until several moons ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.41,0:08:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.70,0:08:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Charity Kindheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.29,0:08:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,She was a well-known costume designer on Bridleway.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.12,0:08:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,She started the Midsummer Theatre Revival
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.50,0:08:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,as a way to share her passion for theatre with the neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.67,0:08:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how busy she was, she always made time for the Revival.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.13,0:08:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But when she moved away to be closer to her grandfillies,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.14,0:08:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,the neighborhood lost the special tradition she had started,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.14,0:08:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and worse, the sense of community it fostered.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.35,0:09:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'm trotting here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.27,0:09:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Nopony else stepped up to take over for Charity?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.90,0:09:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been trying to,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.36,0:09:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,but I've just gotten a last-minute request
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.16,0:09:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,to alter costumes for the cast of My Fair Filly,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.78,0:09:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm afraid I haven't made much progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.62,0:09:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there's just so much to do to bring back the Midsummer Revival,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.66,0:09:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and my flyers haven't attracted a single volunteer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.00,0:09:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Say no more!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.21,0:09:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You finish up your work, and by this time tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.76,0:09:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll be up to your mane in ponies who want to lend a hoof.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.51,0:09:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Applejack and I will make sure of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.72,0:09:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You will?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.18,0:09:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You bet your boots we will!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.35,0:09:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I don't wear boots.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.39,0:09:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I find they chafe my calves when I walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.56,0:09:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just an expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.73,0:09:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So you see, the Method Mares are only available on this one day,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.36,0:09:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and we need all the help we can get with preparation!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.86,0:09:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, not a good time right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.66,0:09:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I saying?\NIt's never a good time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.67,0:10:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.58,0:10:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I got my own problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.38,0:10:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You think I've got hours to dedicate to somepony else's?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.92,0:10:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.34,0:10:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Charity's Midsummer Theatre Revival, such wonderful memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.43,0:10:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So you'll help us?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.98,0:10:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.81,0:10:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I run a very important oat and hay import/export business.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.94,0:10:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't spare even a moment for such things!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.41,0:10:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.62,0:10:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, not at all, darling!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.41,0:10:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's quite lovely!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.25,0:10:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I think she was talkin' about the Midsummer Theatre Revival?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.75,0:10:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I finished the alterations for My Fair Filly,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.34,0:10:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,but I've barely started the costumes for the Revival,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.46,0:10:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and the Method Mares are coming to the park tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.38,0:10:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,for a costume fitting and rehearsal!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.43,0:10:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I could help you with the costumes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.97,0:10:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But what are we going to do about the rest?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.51,0:11:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The park is in desperate need of repairs,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.22,0:11:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and the sets still need to be built!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.73,0:11:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Well I know a thing or two about buildin' and fixin' things.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.56,0:11:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's kinda, well, my thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.19,0:11:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Could be the reason the map called me here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.90,0:11:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, dear?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.03,0:11:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We went out looking for volunteers
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.57,0:11:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,when all the help you need is right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.86,0:11:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.28,0:11:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The map wouldn't have chosen just Applejack and me
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.53,0:11:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,if it was more than we could handle!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.12,0:11:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is going to be just fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.92,0:11:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps I spoke too soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.38,0:11:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh dear, you're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.63,0:11:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you can manage this by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.14,0:11:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there's a lot to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.39,0:11:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,but Rarity's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.64,0:11:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The map wouldn't have called us here
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.06,0:11:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,if we weren't up for the challenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.52,0:11:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You two go on and take care of the costumes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.48,0:11:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll see you at the dress rehearsal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.83,0:12:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it looks bad, but I'm movin' as fast as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.96,0:12:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, we've still got plenty of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.30,0:12:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything's going to be-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.21,0:12:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ehm, excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.59,0:13:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this where the Midsummer Theatre Revival
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.05,0:13:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,is supposed to be, perchance?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.89,0:13:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We're here for the dress rehearsal?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.60,0:13:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes! We've just put the finishing touches on the costumes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.52,0:13:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,At least those look professional.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.40,0:13:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll do a dry run of the play first, and then the fitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.86,0:13:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No, wait! I haven't got a chance to-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.29,0:13:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,...reinforce the stage yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.84,0:13:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to live up to Charity's example,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.93,0:13:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,to bring my neighborhood together again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.56,0:13:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The park is still a mess,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.10,0:13:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,we haven't even thought about what refreshments
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.73,0:13:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,to serve during the performance,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.19,0:13:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and even if we had, we don't have a stage
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.94,0:13:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,for the Method Mares to perform on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.94,0:13:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hopeless...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.57,0:13:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,just hopeless!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.57,0:14:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand. The map summoned us here
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.12,0:14:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,to solve a friendship problem,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.74,0:14:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,we've clearly found it, but why did it send the two of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.41,0:14:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.79,0:14:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure she could have used her magic
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.33,0:14:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,to transform this park in an instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.33,0:14:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been thinkin' the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.09,0:14:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I can at least see why you're here – Coco's your friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.38,0:14:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and you have a knack for costumes and all – but me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.43,0:14:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I was never gonna be able to finish a project this big!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.35,0:14:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll return to Ponyville as failures!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.76,0:14:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Why must this be, Applejack?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.52,0:14:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.02,0:14:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.48,0:14:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Now hold on there. I'm not suggestin' we pack up and go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.02,0:14:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And what are you suggesting-  And what are you suggesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.65,0:14:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm suggestin' we stop worryin' about what we can't do,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.03,0:14:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and start doing what we can!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.41,0:14:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I've got a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.03,0:14:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't be anythin' big or fancy, but it'll be somethin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.08,0:14:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And somethin's gotta be better than nothin', right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.71,0:14:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose so...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.71,0:14:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the spirit! Sorta...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.76,0:15:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright y'all, it's ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.43,0:15:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we go ahead and start?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.02,0:15:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me? I'm Charity Kindheart,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.44,0:15:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here about the open design position!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.27,0:15:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought some samples of my work.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.78,0:15:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.36,0:15:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I had the hardest time finding my way here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.86,0:15:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I just moved here,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.87,0:15:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and I keep getting mixed up by the street names!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.95,0:15:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a map, but I dropped it in a puddle,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.29,0:15:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,which only made the street names harder to read!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.92,0:15:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.09,0:15:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.34,0:15:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I dunno, sugar, looks like some kinda play.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.80,0:15:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, can we stay and watch it please?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.93,0:15:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, can we, can we?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.18,0:15:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh alright, I suppose we could stay for a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.43,0:15:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, but your next appointment is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.94,0:16:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright. Send him in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.65,0:16:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but based on these samples,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.82,0:16:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I just don't think this is the place for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.70,0:16:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get me wrong, these clothes are all exquisite,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.91,0:16:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and well-made, but more theatrical than avant-garde.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.41,0:16:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you considered costume design?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.25,0:16:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a contact on Bridleway!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.25,0:16:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're interested,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.50,0:16:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I can put you in touch with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.09,0:16:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.35,0:16:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Charity, dear, is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.31,0:16:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Mrs. Pearblossom!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.31,0:16:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't see- oops!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.61,0:16:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, let me help you, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.53,0:16:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Are these the costumes you've been working on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.66,0:16:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I was supposed to be finished by now,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.70,0:16:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,but there's just so much to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.74,0:16:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and I still have a few last-minute alterations
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.45,0:16:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,to make before opening night!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.71,0:17:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I couldn't get enough tickets
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.96,0:17:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,for everypony in the neighborhood, I hope Mr.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.96,0:17:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Pearblossom wasn't too disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.55,0:17:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I know Trotter on the Roof is one of his favorites.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.84,0:17:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my dear filly, don't worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.80,0:17:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We're so proud of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.35,0:17:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We shall be with you in spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.77,0:17:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you! You've all made me feel so welcome here,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.60,0:17:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and have become like family to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.27,0:17:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wish I could share this experience with you and the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.36,0:17:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, what's goin' on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.94,0:17:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Midsummer Theatre Revival.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.15,0:17:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The Method Mares are performing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.37,0:17:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The Revival. Mhm, yeah, my pop used to bring me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.16,0:17:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So nice of you to put on this play for the neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.83,0:17:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't have done it without everypony's help!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.50,0:17:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's not Bridleway, but-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.92,0:17:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, pish-tosh! It's perfect, dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.01,0:18:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're such a dear, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.14,0:18:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This is so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.48,0:18:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't seen the neighborhood
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.23,0:18:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,this friendly since Charity moved away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.16,0:18:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, fillies and gentlecolts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.70,0:18:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Please give a warm welcome to the one
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.79,0:18:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,who made this entire event possible, our neighbor, Coco Pommel!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.51,0:18:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you all so much for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.68,0:18:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The Midsummer Theatre Revival was always
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.01,0:18:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,something that meant so much to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.97,0:18:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and it seems it means quite a lot to all of you as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.31,0:18:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I really can't take all the credit, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.19,0:18:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,My dear friends Rarity and Applejack helped me ever so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.61,0:18:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh darling, please, it was just a few costumes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.66,0:19:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw shucks, I just happen to be good with a hammer, is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.24,0:19:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, we had much bigger plans to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.50,0:19:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,When those fell through, we decided to simplify.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.46,0:19:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This here was the result.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.83,0:19:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't be so modest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.25,0:19:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Coco and I were lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.67,0:19:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You bet your boots we were!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.60,0:19:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We just wanted to say how much
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.90,0:19:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,we enjoyed the Midsummer Theatre Revival,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.02,0:19:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and how much it inspired us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.86,0:19:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.24,0:19:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to think that to help my community
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.07,0:19:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to do something big, aheh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.95,0:19:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's face it, in this day and age,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.24,0:19:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,who has the time for such a commitment?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.62,0:19:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But here, you did something as simple as
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.29,0:19:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,building a stage and putting on a play, and, heh,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.71,0:19:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,look at how it's brought everypony together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.92,0:19:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw Coco's flyers for volunteers but didn't think
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.01,0:20:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,anything I'd have time to do would be that useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.76,0:20:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I wish I'd offered to help, even if it was just
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.85,0:20:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,pulling a few weeds, or planting a few flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.64,0:20:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Not sure if you noticed, but the park is far from bein' fixed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.77,0:20:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I imagine if you look around you'll find there's
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.86,0:20:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,lots of little ways for you to get involved
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.61,0:20:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,in changin' this place for the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.07,0:20:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.20,0:20:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't think we'll be alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.91,0:20:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yee-hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.25,0:20:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.92,0:20:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand now! It all makes perfect sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.76,0:20:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.47,0:20:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I know why the map called you here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.14,0:20:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.89,0:20:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If Twilight had used her magic to fix the park,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.27,0:20:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,it wouldn't have fixed the real problem,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.44,0:20:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,which is that these Manehattan ponies didn't think
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.94,0:20:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,they had time to do something for their community!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.48,0:20:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But by building that stage and making sure the play went on,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.69,0:20:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,you showed them that just by doing something small,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.53,0:21:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,you can make a big difference!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.99,0:21:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Well I'll be!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.41,0:21:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems you have more in common
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.91,0:21:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,with the Manehattan ponies than you thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.20,0:21:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Heheh. But, all the same,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.71,0:21:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd sure like to head back to Ponyville on the next train.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.42,0:21:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to check in with Apple Bloom and find out
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.29,0:21:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,how the Sisterhooves Social turned out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.21,0:21:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, absolutely, my dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.67,0:21:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as soon as I stop that pony in the shop over there
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.68,0:21:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,from purchasing that dreadfully hideous scarf!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.22,0:21:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.01,0:21:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You're making a terrible mistake!
